name: Terry Wiliam
description:
I am a Single man, I Live alone, I Love To Smile and never get Angry… I am a Very Kind, Loving, Caring, Romantic, Hard working, Passionate, Honest, Responsible, I never Play Games With peoples Heart… I am a One Woman’s Man…
I Love cooking, swimming, walking along The beach, Camping, reading and writing, meeting New People, Dancing and listening to all kinds of Music…
